{"tid":308833,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"中國足球幾時先出現救世主？","createTime":"2017-07-04T13:44:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-05T00:58:13.000Z","uid":9783,"like":5,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"08f324156292b226c71a52f6b5724b3e340fe230","tid":308833,"uid":9783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T13:44:11.000Z","msg":"如果一個國家有一個重量級球星至少可以係國際場上一戰，好似威爾斯既巴利、冰島既施格臣、南韓既孫興民，或者再之前既星仔，但偏偏中國係02年世界盃之後反而不進則退，近幾年似樣既球員最勁可能已經係武磊、張琳㺬.<br />\n<br />\n到較早幾日加盟西布朗既張玉寧，雖然年輕力壯、有拼勁，但睇翻佢無論係荷甲定國家隊既表現都強差人意，除左商業理由，再無其他原因.<br />\n<br />\n中超不斷升級，對青訓投入既資金亦越黎越多，但國內實力卻無提升，到底出現咩問題？"},{"pid":"21caead525f2b2aa86c65482928092320ce88222","tid":308833,"uid":9783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T13:45:28.000Z","msg":"純足球討論"},{"pid":"8f99231b39799ac600aa53b8f7bd23b8d9692305","tid":308833,"uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T13:46:26.000Z","msg":"中國人既性格，踢得既人比人踢斷曬腳"},{"pid":"6ffe925a67d642ffa1583639048c7d8839a43a9c","tid":308833,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T13:46:37.000Z","msg":"成班錫身"},{"pid":"28082a28375de97c25b66a8b9e7751484ecdfbd3","tid":308833,"uid":46151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T13:46:57.000Z","msg":"其實你講嗰啲國家 都唔止一兩個人踢緊頂級聯賽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加納嗰啲先係真正一人球隊"},{"pid":"2061c08671f1a4f8905539384d047e706d8b3b38","tid":308833,"uid":60506,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T13:48:35.000Z","msg":"邀請siuma加盟"},{"pid":"99cf66cdce3a422528690a33306db38a438a4943","tid":308833,"uid":126314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T13:48:56.000Z","msg":"張玉寧係真天子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n入英超豪門"},{"pid":"d65d28e484196c1338c14c14d2a6cdfcce9aebda","tid":308833,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T13:49:34.000Z","msg":"問我國